    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like no matter what i do it doesn't matter. i'm constantly masking or protecting myself or dealing with the hate or just the exhaustion of it all. it feels like there's no end in sight. like i'm running a race that's rigged against me and i'm just... done. do you think it's even worth it to keep trying when the odds are this bad?",
